nodes.text: Kaya Natari was an employee of Czerka Corporation. The corporation sent Natari to investigate the possibility of using "Archaeological site 75-D", Czerka's name for the abandoned Dantooine Jedi Enclave, for future Czerka Corporation endeavors. Upon entering the ruins, Natari was immediately attacked by beasts, but Natari's security team, endorsed by Keldran, was able to deal with the creatures. In a field journal, Natari recorded that the old site was of no use for Czerka, either monetary or martial.
